column39: We propose to definitively characterise the somatic genetics of ER%2Bve%2C HER2-ve breast cancer through generation of comprehensive catalogues of somatic mutations in 500 cases by high coverage genome sequencing coupled with integrated transcriptomic and methylation analyses.

We propose to definitively characterise the somatic genetics of ER%2Bve%2C HER2-ve breast cancer through generation of comprehensive catalogues of somatic mutations in 500 cases by high coverage genome sequencing coupled with integrated transcriptomic and methylation analyses.
